title: File folder display window

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a file folder display window, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front view of the file folder display window;
FIG. 2 is a rear view of the file folder display window;
FIG. 3 is a left side view of the file folder display window, the right side view being a mirror image thereof;
FIG. 4 is a top view of the file folder display window;
FIG. 5 is a bottom view of the file folder display window; and,
FIG. 6 is a side, top, perspective view of the file folder display window shown attached to a file folder shown in phantom.
The broken line showing of a file folder in FIG. 6 is for illustrative purposes only and forms no part of the claimed design.
